---
---

<!-- Pengumuman - Horizontal Scroll Cards -->
<section class="py-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-gray-800 relative overflow-hidden">
	<div class="absolute inset-0">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-5" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511632765486-a01980e01a18?w=1920&q=80');"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">PENGUMUMAN</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-400">Informasi terbaru untuk jemaat</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="flex overflow-x-auto gap-6 pb-8 snap-x snap-mandatory scrollbar-hide">
			<div class="min-w-[350px] md:min-w-[400px] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-3xl p-8 snap-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl">
				<div class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-1 inline-block mb-4">
					<span class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Juli 2026</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Retreat Pemuda</h3>
				<p class="text-white/90">Tema: "Berani Berbeda". Bergabunglah dalam retreat pemuda yang akan diadakan bulan ini.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="min-w-[350px] md:min-w-[400px] bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-3xl p-8 snap-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl">
				<div class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-1 inline-block mb-4">
					<span class="text-white text-sm font-medium">November 2026</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Perayaan Natal</h3>
				<p class="text-white/90">Persiapan perayaan Natal akan dimulai. Daftarkan diri untuk ikut pelayanan.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="min-w-[350px] md:min-w-[400px] bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-500 rounded-3xl p-8 snap-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl">
				<div class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-1 inline-block mb-4">
					<span class="text-white text-sm font-medium">Setiap Minggu</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Sekolah Minggu</h3>
				<p class="text-white/90">Kelas dibuka setiap minggu. Anak usia 3-12 tahun sangat welcome!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
